係每日返工都必定由8點聽881到10點再轉去Now聽時事全方位<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">I am watching you.</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>一齊打上去佔據大氣電波啊！</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13b9f284c63c9154caaf87378342384aee4ad23d","tid":1489371,"uid":296712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T00:56:19.000Z","msg":"巴打已出院<br />\n一名絲打準備做手術<br />\n另一名絲打深切治療部插喉未醒<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab42ebab790792e8d29ba73aa71f5c04f74b1f7a","tid":1489371,"uid":264871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T00:58:21.000Z","msg":"聽到想喊"},{"pid":"7d93f896b2ba3e55fdbcceeecbb7b7c344cead10","tid":1489371,"uid":296712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"13b9f284c63c9154caaf87378342384aee4ad23d","tid":1489371,"uid":296712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T00:56:19.000Z","msg":"巴打已出院<br />\n一名絲打準備做手術<br />\n另一名絲打深切治療部插喉未醒<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T00:58:35.000Z","msg":"絲打用身擋刀保護人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"021243cfdec5f176148bec676b0676ec7a964a4b","tid":1489371,"uid":93563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T00:59:40.000Z","msg":"各位巴絲加油"},{"pid":"630d8c1690b116dd3903c348a099ee83d46cb483","tid":1489371,"uid":79046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T01:03:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GZQNO1J.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https:/